title: Women Holding Hands Light Skin Tone
description: Two women holding hands, with both having light skin tones. Represents friendship, romance, and close relationships between women.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, two women with light skin tones hold hands, their fingers delicately interlaced, showcasing Apple’s signature soft rounded edges and smooth gradients.  The rendered skin tones are natural and warm, with subtle highlights that suggest realistic lighting, conveying a feeling of closeness and solidarity. This emoji, as seen on Apple devices, is a powerful symbol of friendship, romance, and unity.
